Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管穿什麼都帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H34332E&\bord0\pos(640,265)}今天臨時停業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord1\blur3\3a&H80\pos(1020,715)}{\fad(500,1000)}挽救措施沒用！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江西也!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給我取消
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取消什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨時停業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒必要聽你的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊樂園開業29年來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有發生過毫無預告就停業的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛辛苦苦積累下來的信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然  你竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  能看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次換我出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前裝式的火槍為什麼能連發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫夫路卿  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將毫不知情的來賓攆回去這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼失禮的事情是不可原諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先從外觀下手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛上任的地上人  知道這個遊樂園的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的也有一定道理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就負責去招待來賓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的表演都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正門前的廣場  你去招待來賓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡什麼都沒有  要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就等著看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維護做得很到位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻臭老鼠  工作上還是挺能幹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江同學  需要檢查的地方還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都到齊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在開始部長會議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長話短說  目前有三個課題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先第一個  延長營業時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抱怨  你們是小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  問題在於延長多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那裡沒有夜間營業的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多也就能延長到日落而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先將關門時間從五點推遲到七點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時開始佈置夜間營業的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設備到位後時間延長到九點  就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個  休息日全部取消
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完沒完  給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了週五休息  你們到底想不想幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是愉快的週五啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個屁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才正是撈錢的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  明天開始到7月31日為止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一天假期  明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個  這個最關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到7月31日為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門票以及所有的娛樂設施全都免費
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從經理的立場來說  我反對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢性赤字的本遊樂園沒有這樣的資本了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水電都要花錢的啊  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是職業的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能免費去表演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你職業表演毆打客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候是我的錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管是什麼樣的表演  免費是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要免費過一次  以後再想收錢就難了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦如此  就徹底完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也料到會被反對的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的意見都很有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就統一定為30日元吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定為30日元有什麼依據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座遊樂園明年就是30週年了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以這個名義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算收30日元  跟免費也沒有太大區別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起赤字  現在重要的是客流量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達不到目標的話  以後的赤字也不用談了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  今天的會議到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回自己的崗位去  解散
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30日元  30日元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼  說我們的表演就值30日元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬卡龍你不生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧  反正沒有來賓的話我們就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能不擇手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上台了  點心妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊  音樂妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  轉換心情  去迎接來賓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去的是出島樂園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法只能來這裡結果居然停業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我道歉  你這個山寨貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小武住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是孩子的母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您來阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種玩偶很多人都摸來摸去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能染上奇怪的病菌所以不能摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小武出什麼事了  我就投訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟哦  山寨貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺凌表演來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是火上澆油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是對您寶貝孩子的擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊  完全不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說還能說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這傢伙欺負了  人家受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然對客人施加暴力  真是沒常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教育教育你  把玩偶裝脫掉  山寨貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人就是上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而就算是上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘟囔什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不能踩的紅線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這表情算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不揍你你就不明白是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  搞砸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  那個玩偶不是一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓  裝作沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在這睡著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我是山寨貨的人的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就親身體會一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgotten  Realms  消除記憶的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會醒過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪  這是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你馬上就會適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想適應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然對客人施予暴力  真是聞所未聞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被傳出去  馬上就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會平時就在這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多每年都會搞砸一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你能做到現在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想開除我的話請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  知道自己的立場才這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不為例
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再出問題的話就直接開除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你會開除它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是四棒打者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且因為你的子彈  總算把事情處理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  關於這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個Forgotten  Realms是非常貴重的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一顆要耗費一年時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量有限  請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是這麼貴重的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  那個超疼的子彈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你整天都在用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Painbringer嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個的話30日元10顆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  有些東西不能隨意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才幫大忙了  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做的事情我都會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那這就請你為此脫衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真的要脫衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這泳衣尺度有點大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被性騷擾中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿這種泳衣出去  腦子壞掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看看男性版
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹型姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西爾菲  翅膀忘記拿掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個能拿下來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  畢竟是服裝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服裝?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  好一個破壞別人夢想的遊樂園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江大人  拍我這樣的真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說能拍到你求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起喊  一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘城光輝遊樂園  票價全部30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有精神一點  一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘城光輝遊樂園  票價全部30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉媞琺  笑容太僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再放開點  一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘城光輝遊樂園  票價全部30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千斗  你那根本不叫笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘城光輝遊樂園  票價全部30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能行  能行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙人特利戈  不由自主身體前傾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在計劃之中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  莫夫路居然會允許拉媞琺大人出演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫夫路是拉媞琺大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江西也!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻停止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下流的宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒必要聽你的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然那樣對待拉媞琺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  果然看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個模式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫夫路卿  請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我冷靜?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉媞琺身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然穿成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有說過不願意的話可以不做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是一個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你利用了她這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下是知曉了一切才答應的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我再重複
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續胡鬧會令公主殿下傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是盡可能不要把她帶出空中庭園
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是結界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要告訴三個月後就要離開這裡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下由於一些原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太方便離開設有結界的空中庭園
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個原因是不能說的秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…這件事不太方便多說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這與經營沒有直接關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要把這件事記住就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代理經理  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要你編輯的影片還有一個  抓緊時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
